    • 方法详细资料

      • setCacheAble

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setCacheAble(boolean cacheAble)
        set weather current request is enable cache.

        true for enable cache.
        false for skip the cache queue and go straight to the network.

        when enable cache, you can set setExpiredTime(int) to custom define cache expired time.

      • setDiskCacheSize

public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setDiskCacheSize(int diskCacheSize)

        custom define disk cache size.

      • setExpiredTime

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setExpiredTime(int expiredTime)
        set cache enable time (ms), default value is 0ms, if expired time <= 0 and enable cache, request cache configure will dependence on server response header's "Cache-Control" key.

      • setHeader

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setHeader(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> header)

      • setRetryTimes

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setRetryTimes(int retryTimes)
        set retry times with request, if retry times > 1, request will recall when first request is fail. default value is 1.

      • setTag

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setTag(java.lang.Object tag)

      • setTimeout

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setTimeout(int timeout)
        set time out value, default value is 5000ms.

      • setType

        public BfcRequestConfigure.Builder setType(BfcRequestConfigure.Type type)
        set request type, now support three different type:

        BfcRequestConfigure.Type.STRING default request type, process normal network request.
        BfcRequestConfigure.Type.GZIP gzip enable request, auto unzip gzip response data. Also support normal response, if response header's "Content-Encoding" not include "gzip", this will direct return data as normal request.

        default type is BfcRequestConfigure.Type.STRING.
